<gcds-heading tag="h2">Quick Start</gcds-heading>

<ol class="list-decimal">
  <li>Create <code>.html</code> templates in <code>src/templates/english/</code> or <code>src/templates/french/</code></li>
  <li>Use <code>.njk</code> and <code>.md</code> files for navigation and development pages (won't be copied to gcds-examples)</li>
  <li>Run <kbd>npm run build</kbd> to generate HTML artifacts in <code>_site/</code></li>
  <li>Run <kbd>npm run copy-to-examples</kbd> to copy only <code>.html</code> artifacts to <code>packages/gcds-examples/templates/</code></li>
</ol>

